      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128168;</span><div class="rc-title">Soot or creosote smell</div><div class="rc-desc">Heavy residue from cold-weather use causes persistent odour. Annual cleaning removes it.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#9888;&#65039;</span><div class="rc-title">Annual clean overdue</div><div class="rc-desc">Annual sweeping is essential for Tecoma homes where the fireplace is used heavily through the long cold ranges winter.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#127800;</span><div class="rc-title">Bird nest or debris in the chimney</div><div class="rc-desc">Ranges chimney pots attract nesting birds. We clear blockages and advise on capping.</div></div>
